name: Babbage's Cabbages
description:
The robot operated food truck "Babbage's Cabbages" suffered a quantum detonation while preparing sauerkraut balls. 

Now the universe swaps with another reality and back every ten seconds. Recover the cabbages to save the multiverse.

Jump - W, Space, or Up

Move left/right - A/D or Left/Right

Descend Quickly - S or Down

Ludum Dare Page https://ldjam.com/events/ludum-dare/51/babbages-cabbages

Music by https://freesound.org/people/frankum/sounds/384468/
